<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Omarchy for Developers</title>
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=JetBrains+Mono:wght@300;400;500;600&family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        :root {
            --bg-primary: #0a0a08;
            --bg-secondary: #141412;
            --bg-tertiary: #1e1e1a;
            --bg-card: rgba(20, 20, 18, 0.75);
            --bg-card-solid: #1a1a16;
            --text-primary: #d4cfc4;
            --text-secondary: #8a8578;
            --text-muted: #5a5548;
            --accent-green: #7a9e7a;
            --accent-green-dim: #5a7a5a;
            --accent-amber: #b89a6a;
            --accent-amber-dim: #8a7a5a;
            --border-subtle: rgba(90, 85, 72, 0.2);
            --border-medium: rgba(90, 85, 72, 0.35);
            --shadow-soft: 0 8px 32px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);
            --shadow-glow: 0 0 40px rgba(122, 158, 122, 0.05);
        }

        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Inter', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, sans-serif;
            background: var(--bg-primary);
            color: var(--text-primary);
            min-height: 100vh;
            line-height: 1.7;
            overflow-x: hidden;
        }

        /* Background with the cabin wallpaper */
        .bg-layer {
            position: fixed;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            background: url('https://w.wallhaven.cc/full/5w/wallhaven-5weoz7.png') center/cover no-repeat;
            z-index: -2;
        }

        .bg-overlay {
            position: fixed;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            background: linear-gradient(
                180deg,
                rgba(10, 10, 8, 0.85) 0%,
                rgba(10, 10, 8, 0.70) 30%,
                rgba(10, 10, 8, 0.55) 60%,
                rgba(10, 10, 8, 0.80) 100%
            );
            z-index: -1;
        }

        /* Noise texture overlay */
        .noise {
            position: fixed;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            opacity: 0.03;
            z-index: -1;
            pointer-events: none;
            background-image: url("data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg viewBox='0 0 256 256' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%3E%3Cfilter id='noise'%3E%3CfeTurbulence type='fractalNoise' baseFrequency='0.9' numOctaves='4' stitchTiles='stitch'/%3E%3C/filter%3E%3Crect width='100%25' height='100%25' filter='url(%23noise)'/%3E%3C/svg%3E");
        }

        /* Top bar - like Omarchy's status bar */
        .top-bar {
            position: fixed;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            right: 0;
            height: 32px;
            background: rgba(20, 20, 26, 0.85);
            backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
            -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
            border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-subtle);
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: space-between;
            padding: 0 20px;
            z-index: 100;
            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: var(--text-secondary);
            letter-spacing: 0.3px;
        }

        .top-bar-left {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 12px;
        }

        .workspace-dot {
            width: 6px;
            height: 6px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            background: var(--text-muted);
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }

        .workspace-dot.active {
            background: var(--accent-green);
            box-shadow: 0 0 6px rgba(122, 158, 122, 0.4);
        }

        .top-bar-center {
            position: absolute;
            left: 50%;
            transform: translateX(-50%);
            font-weight: 400;
            color: var(--text-secondary);
        }

        .top-bar-right {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 14px;
        }

        .top-bar-icon {
            width: 14px;
            height: 14px;
            opacity: 0.6;
            transition: opacity 0.2s;
        }

        .top-bar-icon:hover {
            opacity: 1;
        }

        /* Main container */
        .main-container {
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 100px 24px 80px;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
        }

        /* Hero section */
        .hero {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 60px;
        }

        .hero-badge {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 8px;
            padding: 6px 16px;
            background: rgba(122, 158, 122, 0.1);
            border: 1px solid rgba(122, 158, 122, 0.2);
            border-radius: 100px;
            font-size: 12px;
            font-weight: 500;
            color: var(--accent-green);
            letter-spacing: 0.5px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            margin-bottom: 24px;
            backdrop-filter: blur(4px);
        }

        .hero-badge::before {
            content: '';
            width: 6px;
            height: 6px;
            background: var(--accent-green);
            border-radius: 50%;
            box-shadow: 0 0 8px rgba(122, 158, 122, 0.5);
            animation: pulse 2s ease-in-out infinite;
        }

        @keyframes pulse {
            0%, 100% { opacity: 1; transform: scale(1); }
            50% { opacity: 0.5; transform: scale(0.8); }
        }

        .hero h1 {
            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
            font-size: 42px;
            font-weight: 300;
            color: var(--text-primary);
            letter-spacing: -1px;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
            line-height: 1.2;
        }

        .hero h1 span {
            font-weight: 500;
            color: var(--accent-green);
        }

        .hero-subtitle {
            font-size: 16px;
            color: var(--text-secondary);
            font-weight: 300;
            max-width: 480px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        /* Terminal card */
        .terminal-card {
            background: var(--bg-card);
            backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
            -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
            border: 1px solid var(--border-medium);
            border-radius: 14px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: var(--shadow-soft), var(--shadow-glow);
            margin-bottom: 60px;
            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
        }

        .terminal-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 12px 48px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5), 0 0 60px rgba(122, 158, 122, 0.08);
        }

        .terminal-header {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 8px;
            padding: 14px 18px;
            background: rgba(30, 30, 26, 0.6);
            border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-subtle);
        }

        .terminal-dot {
            width: 12px;
            height: 12px;
            border-radius: 50%;
        }

        .terminal-dot.red { background: #5a3a3a; }
        .terminal-dot.yellow { background: #5a5a3a; }
        .terminal-dot.green { background: #3a5a3a; }

        .terminal-title {
            margin-left: 8px;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: var(--text-muted);
            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
            letter-spacing: 0.3px;
        }

        .terminal-body {
            padding: 24px 28px;
            font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', 'Fira Code', monospace;
            font-size: 14px;
            line-height: 2;
        }

        .terminal-line {
            display: flex;
            align-items: flex-start;
            gap: 10px;
            opacity: 0;
            animation: fadeInUp 0.5s ease forwards;
        }

        .terminal-line:nth-child(1) { animation-delay: 0.2s; }
        .terminal-line:nth-child(2) { animation-delay: 0.6s; }
        .terminal-line:nth-child(3) { animation-delay: 1.0s; }
        .terminal-line:nth-child(4) { animation-delay: 1.4s; }
        .terminal-line:nth-child(5) { animation-delay: 1.8s; }

        @keyframes fadeInUp {
            from {
                opacity: 0;
                transform: translateY(8px);
            }
            to {
                opacity: 1;
                transform: translateY(0);
            }
        }

        .terminal-prompt {
            color: var(--accent-green);
            font-weight: 500;
            white-space: nowrap;
            user-select: none;
        }

        .terminal-command {
            color: var(--text-primary);
        }

        .terminal-command .comment {
            color: var(--text-muted);
            font-style: italic;
        }

        .terminal-cursor {
            display: inline-block;
            width: 8px;
            height: 18px;
            background: var(--accent-green);
            margin-left: 2px;
            animation: blink 1s step-end infinite;
            vertical-align: text-bottom;
        }

        @keyframes blink {
            0%, 100% { opacity: 1; }
            50% { opacity: 0; }
        }

        .terminal-divider {
            height: 1px;
            background: var(--border-subtle);
            margin: 20px 0;
        }

        /* GitHub button */
        .github-section {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            padding: 0 28px 28px;
        }

        .github-btn {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 10px;
            padding: 12px 28px;
            background: rgba(122, 158, 122, 0.1);
            border: 1px solid rgba(122, 158, 122, 0.25);
            border-radius: 10px;
            color: var(--accent-green);
            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
            font-size: 14px;
            font-weight: 500;
            text-decoration: none;
            letter-spacing: 0.3px;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            backdrop-filter: blur(4px);
        }

        .github-btn:hover {
            background: rgba(122, 158, 122, 0.18);
            border-color: rgba(122, 158, 122, 0.4);
            transform: translateY(-1px);
            box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(122, 158, 122, 0.1);
        }

        .github-btn svg {
            width: 18px;
            height: 18px;
            fill: currentColor;
        }

        /* Info section */
        .info-section {
            margin-top: 40px;
        }

        .section-header {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 12px;
            margin-bottom: 32px;
        }

        .section-line {
            flex: 1;
            height: 1px;
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--border-medium), transparent);
        }

        .section-line.right {
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, var(--border-medium));
        }

        .section-title {
            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
            font-size: 11px;
            font-weight: 500;
            color: var(--text-muted);
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 2px;
            white-space: nowrap;
        }

        /* Info cards */
        .info-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
            gap: 16px;
        }

        .info-card {
            background: var(--bg-card);
            backdrop-filter: blur(16px);
            -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(16px);
            border: 1px solid var(--border-subtle);
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 24px;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }

        .info-card:hover {
            border-color: var(--border-medium);
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
        }

        .info-card-icon {
            width: 36px;
            height: 36px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            background: rgba(122, 158, 122, 0.08);
            border: 1px solid rgba(122, 158, 122, 0.15);
            border-radius: 10px;
            margin-bottom: 16px;
            font-size: 16px;
        }

        .info-card h3 {
            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
            font-size: 15px;
            font-weight: 500;
            color: var(--text-primary);
            margin-bottom: 8px;
            letter-spacing: -0.2px;
        }

        .info-card p {
            font-size: 13px;
            color: var(--text-secondary);
            line-height: 1.7;
        }

        .info-card ul {
            list-style: none;
            margin-top: 10px;
        }

        .info-card ul li {
            font-size: 13px;
            color: var(--text-secondary);
            padding: 4px 0;
            padding-left: 18px;
            position: relative;
        }

        .info-card ul li::before {
            content: '›';
            position: absolute;
            left: 0;
            color: var(--accent-green);
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        /* Tech tags */
        .tech-tags {
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            gap: 6px;
            margin-top: 14px;
        }

        .tech-tag {
            padding: 4px 10px;
            background: rgba(90, 85, 72, 0.1);
            border: 1px solid rgba(90, 85, 72, 0.15);
            border-radius: 6px;
            font-size: 11px;
            color: var(--text-secondary);
            font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
            transition: all 0.2s;
        }

        .tech-tag:hover {
            border-color: var(--accent-green-dim);
            color: var(--accent-green);
            background: rgba(122, 158, 122, 0.05);
        }

        /* Footer */
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 60px 0 40px;
            color: var(--text-muted);
            font-size: 12px;
            letter-spacing: 0.5px;
        }

        .footer a {
            color: var(--accent-green-dim);
            text-decoration: none;
            transition: color 0.2s;
        }

        .footer a:hover {
            color: var(--accent-green);
        }

        /* Scrollbar */
        ::-webkit-scrollbar {
            width: 8px;
        }

        ::-webkit-scrollbar-track {
            background: var(--bg-primary);
        }

        ::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb {
            background: var(--bg-tertiary);
            border-radius: 4px;
        }

        ::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb:hover {
            background: var(--border-medium);
        }

        /* Selection */
        ::selection {
            background: rgba(122, 158, 122, 0.25);
            color: var(--text-primary);
        }

        /* Responsive */
        @media (max-width: 600px) {
            .hero h1 {
                font-size: 28px;
            }

            .terminal-body {
                padding: 18px 20px;
                font-size: 12px;
            }

            .main-container {
                padding: 80px 16px 60px;
            }

            .top-bar {
                padding: 0 12px;
            }

            .top-bar-center {
                display: none;
            }
        }
    </style>
<base target="_blank">
</head>
<body>
    <div class="bg-layer"></div>
    <div class="bg-overlay"></div>
    <div class="noise"></div>

    <!-- Top Bar -->
    <div class="top-bar">
        <div class="top-bar-left">
            <div class="workspace-dot active"></div>
            <div class="workspace-dot"></div>
            <div class="workspace-dot"></div>
            <div class="workspace-dot"></div>
            <div class="workspace-dot"></div>
        </div>
        <div class="top-bar-center">Omarchy for Developers</div>
        <div class="top-bar-right">
            <svg class="top-bar-icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                <path d="M18.36 6.64a9 9 0 1 1-12.73 0"></path>
                <line x1="12" y1="2" x2="12" y2="12"></line>
            </svg>
            <svg class="top-bar-icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                <path d="M5 12.55a11 11 0 0 1 14.08 0"></path>
                <path d="M1.42 9a16 16 0 0 1 21.16 0"></path>
                <path d="M8.53 16.11a6 6 0 0 1 6.95 0"></path>
                <line x1="12" y1="20" x2="12.01" y2="20"></line>
            </svg>
            <svg class="top-bar-icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                <rect x="2" y="3" width="20" height="14" rx="2" ry="2"></rect>
                <line x1="8" y1="21" x2="16" y2="21"></line>
                <line x1="12" y1="17" x2="12" y2="21"></line>
            </svg>
            <svg class="top-bar-icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                <polyline points="18 15 12 9 6 15"></polyline>
            </svg>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="main-container">
        <!-- Hero -->
        <div class="hero">
            <div class="hero-badge">Available Now</div>
            <h1>Omarchy <span>for Developers</span></h1>
            <p class="hero-subtitle">A pre-configured Arch Linux distribution with Hyprland, built for developers who value keyboard-driven workflows and minimal aesthetics.</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Terminal Card -->
        <div class="terminal-card">
            <div class="terminal-header">
                <div class="terminal-dot red"></div>
                <div class="terminal-dot yellow"></div>
                <div class="terminal-dot green"></div>
                <span class="terminal-title">alacritty — bash</span>
            </div>
            <div class="terminal-body">
                <div class="terminal-line">
                    <span class="terminal-prompt">~</span>
                    <span class="terminal-command">git clone https://github.com/AudiForze/Omarchy-For-Developers</span>
                </div>
                <div class="terminal-line">
                    <span class="terminal-prompt">~</span>
                    <span class="terminal-command">cd Omarchy-For-Developers</span>
                </div>
                <div class="terminal-line">
                    <span class="terminal-prompt">~</span>
                    <span class="terminal-command">chmod +x install.sh</span>
                </div>
                <div class="terminal-line">
                    <span class="terminal-prompt">~</span>
                    <span class="terminal-command">./install.sh</span>
                </div>
                <div class="terminal-line">
                    <span class="terminal-prompt">~</span>
                    <span class="terminal-command"><span class="comment"># Installation complete. Reboot to apply.</span><span class="terminal-cursor"></span></span>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="terminal-divider"></div>
            <div class="github-section">
                <a href="https://github.com/AudiForze/Omarchy-For-Developers" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="github-btn">
                    <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M12 0c-6.626 0-12 5.373-12 12 0 5.302 3.438 9.8 8.207 11.387.599.111.793-.261.793-.577v-2.234c-3.338.726-4.033-1.416-4.033-1.416-.546-1.387-1.333-1.756-1.333-1.756-1.089-.745.083-.729.083-.729 1.205.084 1.839 1.237 1.839 1.237 1.07 1.834 2.807 1.304 3.492.997.107-.775.418-1.305.762-1.604-2.665-.305-5.467-1.334-5.467-5.931 0-1.311.469-2.381 1.236-3.221-.124-.303-.535-1.524.117-3.176 0 0 1.008-.322 3.301 1.23.957-.266 1.983-.399 3.003-.404 1.02.005 2.047.138 3.006.404 2.291-1.552 3.297-1.23 3.297-1.23.653 1.653.242 2.874.118 3.176.77.84 1.235 1.911 1.235 3.221 0 4.609-2.807 5.624-5.479 5.921.43.372.823 1.102.823 2.222v3.293c0 .319.192.694.801.576 4.765-1.589 8.199-6.086 8.199-11.386 0-6.627-5.373-12-12-12z"/></svg>
                    View on GitHub
                </a>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Info Section -->
        <div class="info-section">
            <div class="section-header">
                <div class="section-line"></div>
                <span class="section-title">Configuration</span>
                <div class="section-line right"></div>
            </div>

            <div class="info-grid">
                <div class="info-card">
                    <div class="info-card-icon">🪟</div>
                    <h3>Window Manager</h3>
                    <p>Hyprland with tiling layout, keyboard-driven navigation, and smooth animations. Workspaces 1-9 accessible via <code>SUPER + [1-9]</code>.</p>
                    <div class="tech-tags">
                        <span class="tech-tag">hyprland</span>
                        <span class="tech-tag">wayland</span>
                        <span class="tech-tag">tiling</span>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="info-card">
                    <div class="info-card-icon">🎨</div>
                    <h3>Theme</h3>
                    <p>Dark forest aesthetic with muted greens and warm ambers. Custom GTK, icon, and cursor themes included. Terminal styled with Alacritty.</p>
                    <div class="tech-tags">
                        <span class="tech-tag">gtk</span>
                        <span class="tech-tag">waybar</span>
                        <span class="tech-tag">wofi</span>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="info-card">
                    <div class="info-card-icon">🐍</div>
                    <h3>Python Stack</h3>
                    <p>Modern toolchain with <strong>uv</strong> (Astral), replacing pip, pyenv, and venv. Python 3.13 pre-installed with ruff, pytest, and mypy.</p>
                    <div class="tech-tags">
                        <span class="tech-tag">uv</span>
                        <span class="tech-tag">python3.13</span>
                        <span class="tech-tag">ruff</span>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="info-card">
                    <div class="info-card-icon">🛠️</div>
                    <h3>Developer Tools</h3>
                    <p>Essential CLI tools pre-installed and configured for productivity.</p>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Neovim, tmux, fzf, ripgrep</li>
                        <li>fd, bat, eza, zoxide, starship</li>
                        <li>Docker & Docker Compose</li>
                        <li>Brave Browser, VS Code:</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>

                <div class="info-card">
                    <div class="info-card-icon">⌨️</div>
                    <h3>Key Bindings</h3>
                    <p>All workflows are keyboard-first. No mouse required for daily tasks.</p>
                    <ul>
                        <li><code>SUPER + Return</code> — Terminal</li>
                        <li><code>SUPER + ALT + Space</code> — Launcher</li>
                        <li><code>SUPER + W</code> — Close window</li>
                        <li><code>SUPER + SHIFT + R</code> — Reload config</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>

                <div class="info-card">
                    <div class="info-card-icon">🔒</div>
                    <h3>Security</h3>
                    <p>Full disk encryption with LUKS. Auto-login after decryption. Secure Boot and TPM disabled for compatibility.</p>
                    <div class="tech-tags">
                        <span class="tech-tag">luks</span>
                        <span class="tech-tag">encryption</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Footer -->
        <div class="footer">
            <p>Built with care for the Omarchy community · <a href="https://github.com/AudiForze">@AudiForze</a></p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
